description: Che Grill food truck wants to share with you our love of homemade, simple Argentine food; the kind you want to have every day.  Because we're a young group, a food truck seemed a great idea to bring directly to you quality grilled meats, fresh baked bread and empanadas all made with wholesome ingredients.A sizzling Argentine style cut steak drizzled with tipical “chimichurri” sauce will transport you to Argentina.  We’re importers of flavors and you will have a chance to taste them all in our menu, including signature sauces you will not find anywhere else.Share a good time with us when we roll into your neighborhood, and enjoy what we have prepared with imagination...
name: Che Grill
